    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >BlightFog is a short, narrative driven RPG, where you travel across a post apocalyptic world on a bike while taking care of an infant.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230290/extras/8642b6f065ac50c8ef337a035a023926.webp?t=1758467221\" width=600 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On the way you will meet other anthropomorphic characters. Solve conflicts and build relationships through dialogues. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230290/extras/f7306381dd89a21bad9a795c1ac28d96.poster.avif?t=1758467221\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230290/extras/f7306381dd89a21bad9a795c1ac28d96.webm?t=1758467221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230290/extras/f7306381dd89a21bad9a795c1ac28d96.mp4?t=1758467221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Allocate resources between you and the child, find unique items that will influence dialogues and give you new ways to approach different situations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your goal is to save the child's mother and get them both to safety.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230290/extras/ed18d3680325b07a2c9ab1d52354e783.poster.avif?t=1758467221\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230290/extras/ed18d3680325b07a2c9ab1d52354e783.webm?t=1758467221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230290/extras/ed18d3680325b07a2c9ab1d52354e783.mp4?t=1758467221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you chose the longer and safer paths, or risk to save time and fuel and take the shorter but more dangerous ones?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will you let the child starve or sacrifice your own well-being for him? Will you be a pretend-hero, a coward or a fuel-drinking madman who refuses to wear clothes?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230290/extras/f303e9504ecf651303e5628f0480f8f2.poster.avif?t=1758467221\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230290/extras/f303e9504ecf651303e5628f0480f8f2.webm?t=1758467221\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230290/extras/f303e9504ecf651303e5628f0480f8f2.mp4?t=1758467221\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3230290/extras/ddce66bdb3aafab1ef9cfe428b904ddc.webp?t=1758467221\" width=600 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Story heavy RPG where you can: drink fuel, run around naked and destroy the world (maybe)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game remembers your choices</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose the safe or fast paths</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet different antropomorphic characters and build relationships with them</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Light resource management</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple endings</p></li></ul>",
